name: Moon Moon
description: Moon Moon ($MOON) is a community-driven memecoin inspired by the legendary 2013 “Moon Moon” internet meme — the clumsy, lovable wolfdog who always missteps yet wins the heart of the pack. $MOON channels this spirit into crypto, building a movement that blends humor, relatability, and inclusivity. The project’s purpose is to unite underdogs, misfits, and meme lovers through shared culture, fair distribution, and transparent development. More than just a token, Moon Moon aims to foster a lasting community where everyone can “run with the pack,” laugh at the chaos, and chase gains together.
